init_state.contents:
Solve the math problem in small steps.The nine points of this grid are equally spaced horizontally and vertically.  The distance between two neighboring points is 1 unit.  What is the area, in square units, of the region where the two triangles overlap?

[asy]
size(80);
dot((0,0)); dot((0,1));dot((0,2));dot((1,0));dot((1,1));dot((1,2));dot((2,0));dot((2,1));dot((2,2));
draw((0,0)--(2,1)--(1,2)--cycle, linewidth(0.6));
draw((2,2)--(0,1)--(1,0)--cycle, linewidth(0.6));
[/asy]

